# imputacao
W  = matrix(0,dim(SNP)[1],dim(SNP)[2])


for (j in 1:ncol(SNP)) {
  # cat('j = ', j, '\n')
  W[, j] = ifelse(is.na(SNP[, j]), mean(SNP[, j], na.rm = TRUE), SNP[, j])
}
